      <p>
        GitHub Pages hosts this explainer, but the real Astropress admin is backed by the canonical database
        model and provider-neutral runtime adapters.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>non-technical users edit pages, posts, media, redirects, comments, users, and translations in admin</li>
        <li>git sync is optional export/import infrastructure, not the primary editing path</li>
